      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been well-loved and is in really solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. It\u2019s been a fantastic companion for me, and I know you\u2019ll love it too. Perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway\u2014come take it for a spin!",
