    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals. The suspension remains composed via Bilstein dampers, providing excellent damping frequency and roll stiffness. Rolling on staggered Style 67 alloys wrapped in high-performance rubber, this chassis offers the communicative feedback and neutral balance enthusiasts demand. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with documented valve adjustments and a clean underside.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
