    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, with only the minor, superficial character marks consistent with responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting; the seats are firm and comfortable, the carpets have been kept under seasonal mats, and every button and feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car is mechanically sound, having followed a strict schedule of preventative maintenance. It starts promptly, idles quietly, and delivers a smooth, responsive driving experience on both city streets and highways. With a clean title and a documented service history, this car is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
