    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It runs beautifully and has been well-loved over the years, so it's still in really solid shape for its next owner. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
