      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated mill utilizes six individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including essential subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure variable valve timing remains within factory tolerances. The limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load, while the suspension retains its original kinematic precision. This M3 presents in solid mechanical health with minor cosmetic patina, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
